00:53:24.980 --> 00:53:29.100
I think that it was
clear in the crisis

00:53:29.100 --> 00:53:32.160
that we really did not
understand the system.

00:53:32.160 --> 00:53:34.380
And that's partly
why they said that we

00:53:34.380 --> 00:53:36.710
need to bring derivative
trading into the light

00:53:36.710 --> 00:53:40.070
because that's where a
lot of risk was hidden.

00:53:40.070 --> 00:53:41.940
So supposedly there
are regulations

00:53:41.940 --> 00:53:46.200
to try to reduce the
capacity of those markets.

