if you would figure out

00:57:23.490 --> 00:57:27.220
how to do a 21st century
Glass-Steagall, for governance

00:57:27.220 --> 00:57:30.710
and for better
regulation of the pieces.

00:57:30.710 --> 00:57:33.630
